### The Hitchhiker's Guide to Graduate School Applications in the US ###

Description:	
	This is a guide in Turkish for applications to PhD programs in US. Guide also includes the procedures and suggestions before and after the application period. 
	
Authors: 
	Onur Albayrak
	Ahmet Demir
	Ugur Guney
	Ismail Volkan Inlek
	Bugra Kaytanli
	Alp Sipahigil
	Tuna Toksoz

Editor:
	Tolga Suna

Source file is created and maintained by: 
